{"tid":668699,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Call of duty black ops 4","createTime":"2018-05-18T00:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:23:08.000Z","uid":51330,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4af691fabdda5c8f01e5d3248be8671ec435e0","tid":668699,"uid":51330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=rd_2lwp1rQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drd_2lwp1rQU&d=sYyeQcIbHTNM7RPHhJDkp5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=ef87993b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=rd_2lwp1rQU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ooyjaVdt-jA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DooyjaVdt-jA&d=sYyeQcIbHTNM7RPHhJDkp5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3561a3ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ooyjaVdt-jA</a><br />\nBlack ops 4 所有情報大綱總整理。<br />\n<br />\n因為要睡覺了，懶得一個個發，直接作總整理。<br />\n多人模式角色明天再發一篇。<br />\n<br />\n黑色行動4會有Beta，預購得到Beta資格。<br />\n黑色行動4PC版本確定登錄暴雪戰網(<a href=\"http://Bettle.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBettle.net&d=sYyeQcIbHTNM7RPHhJDkp5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=563f8d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bettle.net</a>)。<br />\n黑色行動4PC有專屬伺服器。<br />\n暴雪團隊有幫助開發黑色行動4。<br />\n本作沒有傳統單人劇情，故事將聚焦在多人角色的背景故事。<br />\n本作不能二段跳或攀岩走壁的動作，完全&quot;腳踏實地&quot;。<br />\n黑色行動2的League Play回歸。<br />\n專家角色回歸，一樣會有特殊能力。<br />\n槍枝會有新的後座力系統，自己要預測後座力造成的飄動。<br />\n不能自動回血，要自己用血包。<br />\n玩家有150血量，而非傳統的100血量。<br />\n黑色行動4的擊殺計算跟以往不同，例如我對敵人造成100傷害，隊友對敵人造成50傷害，隊友跟我都會算成1擊殺。<br />\n其中一名角色叫Crash，類似補師的角色。<br />\n新小地圖系統叫Fog of War，玩家有一定可見度，<br />\n殭屍模式將會有三張地圖。<br />\n殭屍模式會有新的主角群，舊主角群會在&quot;Blood of the Dead&quot;地圖登場。<br />\n其中一張地圖(&ldquo;Voyage of the Despair&rdquo;)確定是鐵達尼號，另一張地圖(&ldquo;IX&rdquo;)類似羅馬鬥技場。<br />\n殭屍模式會有大量客製化功能，玩家可以自訂規則。<br />\n殭屍模式支援AI隊友。<br />\n新的大逃殺模式&quot;Black Out&quot;。<br />\n&quot;Black Out&quot;地圖比核彈鎮大1500倍。<br />\n所有黑色行動系列角色都可以使用，包刮殭屍模式的角色和裝備。<br />\n&quot;Black Out&quot;會有載具，包含海陸空。<br />\n轉巴哈:<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=05371&amp;snA=23328&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=5&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D05371%26snA%3D23328%26bpage%3D1%26top%3D5%26ltype%3D&d=sYyeQcIbHTNM7RPHhJDkp5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=be0380ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=05371&amp;snA=23328&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=5&amp;ltype=</a>"},{"pid":"66d9bc606a7d6b7733bbd0f354c29871f1627b47","tid":668699,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"又大逃殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎今年大多數fps都加呢d mode"},{"pid":"87f9b487f78800b5d578799c3531be19360e6fcc","tid":668699,"uid":10571,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"單人劇情冇埋,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744f61d4a6d4ec6e1f414e8010f07f3610457379","tid":668699,"uid":17616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"真實版overwatch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e142f3a7ec8567dcc6b36c93b17f7ea3d0001d2","tid":668699,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"ddc40b75d671436a16d8752017b41a0143fcd084","tid":668699,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"本作沒有傳統單人劇情，故事將聚焦在多人角色的背景故事。<br />\n<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"89f8692bc215c6bfeba34f9eacd878f0b46555c6","tid":668699,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f9b487f78800b5d578799c3531be19360e6fcc","tid":668699,"uid":10571,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"單人劇情冇埋,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"